{"tid":994792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1月27日年廿二收晒爐先反水貨狗, 民主黨不如年初一先黎搞遊行啦","createTime":"2019-01-25T03:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T08:10:09.000Z","uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1574e4f7b750317d71507bb47e3d0fcb723c61","tid":994792,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rO9S4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rO9S4Z.jpg&h=3166e38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痴撚線真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Evw0fjn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvw0fjn.jpg&h=22d860fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">同場加映本土鼻祖范國威2015 指出比位人入邊個最開心</div><br />\n<br />\n身兼「香港本土」發起人的新民主同盟立法會議員范國威，接受電台訪問時表示，周日的反水貨客示威，有示威者指罵並非水貨客人士，出現誤中副車的情況，令示威活動失焦受政府譴責，認為對示威活動幫倒忙。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，示威手法令情況弄巧反拙，認為行動應針對政府，示威者如果鬧錯人，出現推撞和指罵就應道歉，又指政府政策失誤亦應受到譴責。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，如政府仍不調整旅遊政策，港人依然受壓，類似的抗爭會持續，但他期望示威者認清目標，不要再誤中副車，令示威行動失去焦點，讓政府有口實，污名化示威。"},{"pid":"b64dba896f329f31d4e3f37524a86cbd770cb1a2","tid":994792,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95f4d8a0c4230d8dff67110c6c10ea4b93cb7c9","tid":994792,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C9rcwoLU0AAERU9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC9rcwoLU0AAERU9.jpg&h=e92f4978&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}